{"id":61002,"title":"Robotic thymectomy for thymic neoplasms.","abstract":"Robotic thymectomy has been well described for the management of myasthenia gravis and thymic masses. Both short- and long-term safety and efficacy have been demonstrated. Surgical approaches vary, but the technique for thymic dissection and excision is universal. ","date":"2014-04-30","categories":"Hemic and Lymphatic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24780424","annotations":[{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.5184,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Myasthenia gravis","weight":0.271135,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Myasthenia_gravis"},{"name":"Neoplasm","weight":0.160714,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neoplasm"},{"name":"Thymus","weight":0.113797,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thymus"},{"name":"Efficacy","weight":0.11349,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Efficacy"},{"name":"Thymectomy","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thymectomy"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Dissection","weight":0.0269662,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dissection"},{"name":"Robotics","weight":0.0227187,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robotics"},{"name":"Mass (liturgy)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mass_(liturgy)"},{"name":"Safety","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Safety"},{"name":"Universal health care","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Universal_health_care"},{"name":"Short film","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Short_film"}]}
